// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1385 — Mass File Rename (ransomhouse)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 6027769a-ea1a-52bf-874b-91cc5bf3d349

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
